description:
This minecraft tutorial will show you how to format the text inside a book. This means you can add different colors, bold, italic, underline, dash through and other effects to the text in your books. It requires no mods and works in SMP.

Youtube does not allow special symbols in its video descriptions.

Formatting Key
k - Spinning
l - Bold
m - Strikethrough
n - Underline
0 - Italic
r - Reset

Color
0 - Black
1 - Blue
2 - Green
3 - Cyan
4 - Red
5 - Purple
6 - Gold
7 - Light Grey
8 - Grey
9 - Light Blue
a - Lime
b - Aqua
c - Light Red
d - Magenta
e - Yellow
f - White
